description:
Thank you all for an amazing year, in this New Years special we've put together all the Bible In a Nutshell videos of 2023 in one so you can enjoy it all in one video! 

Story of Jesus Christ - 00:00
Story of Noah's Ark - 02:26
Story of Moses - 04:40
Story of Adam & Eve - 07:12
Crucifixion & Resurrection of Jesus Christ - 09:46
Story of David & Goliath - 12:55
Birth of Jesus Christ - 15:04
New Year Message - 17:21

A big shoutout to all our supporters and loyal subscribers. Your constant encouragement and love make our journey through the Bible stories so special. We're grateful for each one of you and excited to make more videos for you in 2024! 

Happy New Year,
The Nutshell Team

Support us by hitting the SUBSCRIBE button, giving us a thumbs up, comment your thoughts below and share this video with your friends and family! Every like, share and comment helps us bring more videos your way! 

Check out Bible In a Nutshell Music!
https://www.youtube.com/@BibleNutshellsMusic/featured

Check out our other Story Telling channels! 
History In a Nutshell - https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCGfKOG9OV7nJxVv4NkSrccw
Scared In a Nutshell - https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCsKv9vB-9aaawWTMKJUSNiA

Listen to our music on Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/artist/2d4Pm0Zsusyh0gVRIC6KlH

While we strive for historical and factual accuracy, please note that these cinematic recreations may involve dramatisation and should not be considered wholly precise in every detail. Our goal is to present these timeless stories in an engaging, visually appealing way that simplifies complex narratives, making them accessible and enjoyable for all audiences.
